JIRA Service Desk includes the magical ability to trigger a workflow transition on comment (Waiting for Customer > Ready for Support). This is the primary piece missing from standard JIRA that would make it most useful for service desks. Non-technical users shouldn't be bothered to re-assign or manually transition tickets after providing updates.

Beyond comments, it could be useful to have the ability to trigger workflow transition based on other built-in system events or user-defined custom events (Issue Updated, Issue Assigned especially).

I envision an intuitive way to include this into the existing workflow editor with an optional "Events" tab on the Add Workflow Transition page for a workflow step.

